Package com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.manager

Class GenericManager<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyberfront.crdt.CRDTManager
      • com.cyberfront.crdt.GenericCRDTManager<T>
        • com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.manager.GenericManager<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the POJO the CRDT will manage
    public class GenericManager<T>
extends GenericCRDTManager<T>
    The Class GenericManager provides a simple mechanism for managing a POJO as a CRDT. It supports the basic CRUD operations on POJO's. Initial instantiation of the manager must include the initial value of the POJO.
